claim.claim-text:
1. A capacitor producing method comprising:
forming a capacitor by depositing a bottom electrode, a thin-film dielectric, and a top electrode on a substrate;
detecting defects, including particles and electrical short-circuits between the bottom electrode and the top electrode, before dividing the capacitor into a plurality of capacitor cells;
storing defects information representing the defects detected by the defect detecting operation; and
removing the defects.

3. A capacitor producing method comprising:
forming a capacitor by depositing a bottom electrode, a thin-film dielectric, and a top electrode on a substrate;
detecting defects, including particles and electrical short-circuits between the bottom electrode and the top electrode, before dividing the capacitor into a plurality of capacitor cells;
adjusting capacitor cell positions indicating positions of the capacitor cells; and
removing the defects.
